1. This Order may be cited as the Public Health (Alcohol) Act 2018 

(Commencement) Order 2023.

title: (insofar as it is not already in operation) of the Public Health (Alcohol) Act
heading: 2. The 22nd day of May 2026 is appointed as the day on which section 12
text_raw:
2. The 22nd day of May 2026 is appointed as the day on which section 12 
(insofar as it is not already in operation) of the Public Health (Alcohol) Act 
2018 (No. 24 of 2018) comes into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

18 May, 2023. 

STEPHEN DONNELLY, 
Minister for Health. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 26th May, 2023.
